meta {
  name: 11 Gecersiz attachment magic-byte - 415
  type: http
  seq: 11
}

post {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/tickets/{{emergencyTicketId}}/attachments
  body: multipartForm
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Authorization: Bearer {{opsToken}}
}

body:multipart-form {
  attachmentType: OTHER
  file: @file(fixtures/fake-image.jpg)
}

assert {
  res.status: eq 415
  res.body.error.code: eq ATTACHMENT_UNSUPPORTED_TYPE
}

docs {
  fake-image.jpg uzantisi .jpg olan duz metindir: beyan edilen content
  type image/jpeg olsa da magic-byte dogrulamasi JPEG/PNG/WEBP imzasi
  bulamaz ve 415 doner. MIME kontrolu yetki kontrolunden ONCE
  calistigindan istek OPERATIONS token'iyla da ayni sonucu verir; gecici
  dosya temizlenir, DB kaydi olusmaz.
}
